snippet.title: Loggerhead Prologue Demo - Trailer
snippet.description:
This is a trailer for a free playable demo of Affordable Cat's upcoming game Loggerhead. Loggerhead prologue is a PS1 era inspired Survival Horror set in Australia during the 1980's featuring Fixed Camera Angles, Tank Controls and Terrible Voice Acting.

You can download the demo now
 
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1762850/Loggerhead/
Itch.io: https://affordable-cat.itch.io/loggerhead

The prologue chapter follows Gary and Sharon who opt to spend a fishing weekend at Boggarogga Creek a condemned campsite to save a few dollarydoo's - what they didn't bank on way maybe the rumors surrounding the closure were true.

Loggerhead prologue demo will be available for free download on Steam and itch.io very soon!

Trailer Music: Huge thanks to Karl Kasey @WhiteBatAudio his work is amazing!
